cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL 

The paper proposes an approach to estimating the transferability of deep networks, especially those handling vision tasks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also deals with deep learning and knowledge transfer, which are common topics in sub-categories such as cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper mentions no human annotations, which suggests that it may also be relevant to sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language).
